  "detailed_description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >ESCAPE ABANDONED SPACE STATION WITH FRIENDS</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1591130/extras/d92eaefbbeeb9d36dd517d71df252ea2.poster.avif?t=1619474090\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1591130/extras/d92eaefbbeeb9d36dd517d71df252ea2.webm?t=1619474090\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1591130/extras/d92eaefbbeeb9d36dd517d71df252ea2.mp4?t=1619474090\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><i>Try it solo or with your friends! Online <strong>multiplayer for up to 4 players</strong>. The best thing - you don't have to stress over time. After all... that is just you and the everlasting cosmos.  </i><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >EXPLORE AND INTERACT</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1591130/extras/91efb03d18639108e75a637b85843ec5.poster.avif?t=1619474090\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1591130/extras/91efb03d18639108e75a637b85843ec5.webm?t=1619474090\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1591130/extras/91efb03d18639108e75a637b85843ec5.mp4?t=1619474090\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><i><strong>Clues can be hidden</strong> in the most unexpected places. You never know what the mysteries of the space station have prepared for you!</i><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >BE PREPARED TO GET YOUR HANDS DIRTY </h2> <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1591130/extras/310d63dd6a9d802c38e7753f3673d869.poster.avif?t=1619474090\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1591130/extras/310d63dd6a9d802c38e7753f3673d869.webm?t=1619474090\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1591130/extras/310d63dd6a9d802c38e7753f3673d869.mp4?t=1619474090\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><i>When your life depends on it, you have to give it your best. <strong>The solution often turns out more beautiful than the puzzle.</strong></i><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >DONT FORGET TO EXPERIMENT</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1591130/extras/490d4293cec81fedf853a11a28d46757.poster.avif?t=1619474090\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1591130/extras/490d4293cec81fedf853a11a28d46757.webm?t=1619474090\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1591130/extras/490d4293cec81fedf853a11a28d46757.mp4?t=1619474090\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><i>Not every puzzle is intended to be solved. Some are in place to test your limits. Others are, in fact, not puzzles at all.</i>",
